==[[Scottish Gaelic]]==

===Noun===
'''galla''' {{f}}
#''Offensive'', a [[bitch]].

===Examples===

* ''"Càr na Galla!"'' "[[Damn]]ed/[[bloody]] car!" (lit. "Car of the Bitch!")
* ''"Siùrsach na Galla!"'' "[[Fuck]]ing bitch!" (lit. "Whore of the Bitch!")
* ''"Thalla dhan Taigh na Galla."'' "Go to Hell." (lit. "Go to the House of the Bitch.")

